{"tid":2255874,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"乞客已經癲到去餐廳要Tap water 都唔撚得","createTime":"2020-10-24T02:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T03:58:05.000Z","uid":7814,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"69af2708710d634ac4ed82b9f25709fb02787b2f","tid":2255874,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T02:26:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1448245808767974/posts/2694584527467423/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1448245808767974%2Fposts%2F2694584527467423%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vDDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=0207840f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1448245808767974/posts/2694584527467423/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n#餐廳Hack105<br />\n<br />\n根據非正式統計，百分之五十飲用餐廳免費Tap水的客人曾因侍應待慢而差點在餐廳渴死😱。其實每間餐廳內均設有任飲的自助tap水區，客人可與三五知己一齊舉杯進入私隱度極高的Tap水自助區，慢慢暢飲Free Flow新鮮水喉水🥂。人有三急時，更能快人一步立即到達廁格暢快暢快💦💦！<br />\n<br />\n#餐廳提供嘅Tap水未必有過濾器<br />\n#有裝嘅過濾器可能用咗幾年都無換過<br />\n#喺屋企都會選擇飲用煲過嘅水<br />\n#然後去餐廳飲水喉水💩🤡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNKhaaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNKhaaU.jpg&h=bf049763&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"403ce68b82988c95370580e2c4604358e7c09b4e","tid":2255874,"uid":237625,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T02:49:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲Page On9到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫杯水都要屌客 睇啲Comment 啲MK侍應仲以為自己好威威<br />\n幫你洗埋碗好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a9652796917aee34dcab97a60ab51959c6f67b","tid":2255874,"uid":125017,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T02:52:28.000Z","msg":"唔想做佢生意咪趕佢走囉<br />\n做乜鳩"},{"pid":"f62c051172471c585359f0b02ddb5a6bee624536","tid":2255874,"uid":85117,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"403ce68b82988c95370580e2c4604358e7c09b4e","tid":2255874,"uid":237625,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy"